        <item>
            <title>英國 AI 虛擬女友每月被求婚廿次    AI 公司年賺 280 萬</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/british-ai-girlfriend/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=british-ai-girlfriend</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/british-ai-girlfriend/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 09:00:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI 女友]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI 虛擬女友]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Foxy AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[虛擬女友]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1216602</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>英國科技公司 Foxy AI 近日開發了一個金髮碧眼的 AI 女郎模型「Lexi Love」。這個 AI 女友會收費與粉絲聊天，而「Lexi Love」的訂閲者更為 Foxy AI 創下 36 萬美元（約港幣 281.63 萬元）年營收的佳績。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/405512259_1103124064-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/405512259_1103124064-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/405512259_1103124064.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p>「Lexi Love」由英國公司 Foxy AI 創造，於 2023 年 6 月面世，是一個可以陪伴有需要人士，向他們提供調情聊天服務的 AI 模式。至今 Lexi Love 月入高達 3 萬美元（約港幣 23.47 萬元）。Lexi 能夠説 30 多種語言，可付費短訊和語音訊息服務，如果用戶要求，Lexi 甚至可傳送性感照片給用戶。據 Lexi 個人簡介描述，她是個 21 歲女孩，喜歡玩鋼管舞、瑜伽及沙灘排球。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240123172710-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240123172710-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240123172710.jpg 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419348285_1121867832-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419348285_1121867832-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419348285_1121867832.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-1-1-597x580.jpg" alt="" width="597" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-1-1-597x580.jpg 597w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-1-1.jpg 926w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 597px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Foxy AI 的官方網站可以看到各種有關 Lexi Love 的資料，圖片來源：<a href="https://foxy.ai/lexi-love/">Foxy AI</a></p><p>據外媒《Economic Times》引述 Foxy AI 發言人指，Lexi Love 非常擅長與粉絲聊天，與不少付費用戶建立聯繫，有些用戶甚至誤會 Lexi Love 是真實人物，Foxy AI 每個月都會收到逾 20 封向 Lexi Love 求婚的信件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419984534_3430198152-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419984534_3430198152-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/419984534_3430198152.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p>據外媒《New York Times》報道，Foxy AI 行政總裁 Sam Emara 表示「Lexi Love」嘗試打破障礙，改變人類和 AI 互動方式；Sam Emara 更稱 Lexi 是旗下最成功的 AI ，開發之初就是希望成為「完美女朋友」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1216628" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/418754167_8393716612-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/418754167_8393716612-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/418754167_8393716612.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/us/meet-lexi-love-ai-model-that-receives-20-proposals-per-month-this-is-virtual-love/articleshow/106994666.cms?from=mdr">Economic Times</a>、<a href="https://nypost.com/2024/01/18/lifestyle/model-lexi-love-makes-360k-a-year-sexting-men-but-theres-one-problem/">New York Post</a>、<a href="https://bnnbreaking.com/tech/ai-ml/lexi-love-the-ai-model-earning-30000-a-month-as-a-virtual-girlfriend/">BNN Breaking</a>、<a href="https://www.instagram.com/lexilove.x/">lexilove.x@Instagram</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/19/openai-gpt-store-2/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】GPT Store 正式開放 ChatGPT AI 女朋友 + 一張相幫你諗食譜</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/07/meta-imagine/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Meta 生成式 AI 繪圖　多種畫風選擇 + 「手指」表現不俗</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/determinant-shirts-for-everywhere/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">生成式 AI 試衫突破想像　DETERMINANT 推出「61 Shirts For Everywhere」企劃</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/british-ai-girlfriend/ai/">英國 AI 虛擬女友每月被求婚廿次    AI 公司年賺 280 萬</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
